record.field: Current quantity of products. In a context with a single Stock Location, this includes goods stored at this Location, or any of its children. In a context with a single Warehouse, this includes goods stored in the Stock Location of this Warehouse, or any of its children. stored in the Stock Location of the Warehouse of this Shop, or any of its children. Otherwise, this includes goods stored in any Stock Location with 'internal' type.
Cost used for stock valuation in standard price and as a first price to set in average/fifo. Also used as a base price for pricelists. Expressed in the default unit of measure of the product.
